            <title>[PIG-1419] Remove &quot;user.name&quot; from JobConf</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-1419</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In hadoop security, hadoop will use kerberos id instead of unix id. Pig should not set &quot;user.name&quot; entry in jobconf. This should be decided by hadoop.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
